column2: SELECT u.up_name as name, /* PhotoObj table parameters*/ &&&&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, round(p.u,#) as PhotoOb_u,round(p.g,#) as PhotoOb_g,round(p.r,#) as PhotoOb_r, round(p.i,#) as PhotoOb_i,round(p.err_u,#) as err_u, p.type, /*specObj table parameters*/ s.class, s.subClass, round(s.z,#) as spec_redshift /* Photomtric redshift table parameters*/ FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoObjAll p ON p.objID = x.objID left JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON s.bestobjid = x.objID ORDER BY x.up_id&&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
